Package org.cloudsimplus.traces.azure

Class VmTypeRecord

java.lang.Object
org.cloudsimplus.traces.azure.VmTypeRecord
public class VmTypeRecord extends Object
Class representing a VM type record. It follows the schema of the AzureTracesForPacking2020 dataset presented in: https://github.com/Azure/AzurePublicDataset/blob/master/AzureTracesForPacking2020.md
Since:
CloudSim Plus 7.3.2
Author:
Pavlos Maniotis
